727777f-b.text:
Oueens Boulevard (foreground, not seen), at the S. W. corner of Seventy-fifth Avenue (formerly Atom Place), showing the home of David Springsteen in a set of two views. It was still owned by the family
in 1924. The house was demolished in October 1928.
1922.
View 2: July 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
